      "id": "plane_crash",
      "bullet_type": "none",
      "text": "Gather the nine story assets from the <i>Expedition Team</i> encounter set, shuffle them, and choose one of them at random. The chosen character was killed in the plane crash. In the Expedition Team section of the Campaign Log, cross of their name. Record in the Campaign Log <i>(character's name) was killed in the plane crash.</i>\n"
